<h1>Storage quota warning</h1>
<p>Hi {{name}},</p>
<p>You've used <strong>{{usagePercent}}%</strong> of your storage quota.</p>
<p>Used: {{formatBytes usedBytes}} / {{formatBytes limitBytes}}</p>
<!-- TODO: Add a visual progress bar using inline CSS (table-based for email compatibility) -->
<p>Consider deleting unused assets or upgrading your plan.</p>
<p><a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/settings/usage">View Usage</a></p>
